    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You need to include a jar that this class exists in.  You can find it <a href=\"https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/com.google.code.findbugs/jsr305\" rel=\"noreferrer\">here</a></p>\n\n<p>If using Maven, you can add the following dependency declaration:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"lang-xml prettyprint-override\"><code>&lt;dependency&gt;\n  &lt;groupId&gt;com.google.code.findbugs&lt;/groupId&gt;\n  &lt;artifactId&gt;jsr305&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n  &lt;version&gt;3.0.2&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>and for Gradle:</p>\n\n<pre><code>dependencies {\n  testImplementation 'com.google.code.findbugs:jsr305:3.0.2'\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1217553,
      "reputation" : 2850,
      "user_id" : 1184842,
      "user_type" : "registered",
