  "title" : "Can&#39;t find @Nullable inside javax.annotation.*",
  "body" : "<p>I want use <code>@Nullable</code>  annotation to  eliminate <code>NullPointerExceptions</code>.\nI found some tutorials on the net, I noticed that this annotation comes from the package <code>javax.annotation.Nullable</code>;\nbut when I import it a compilation error is generated: cannot find symbol</p>\n"
